Actress, Mercy Johnson who is also into the fitness business has started a cooking show and her husband is giving her the necessary support. Mercy Johnson and Prince Okojie Actress Mercy Johnson and her husband, Prince Odi Okojie shared a romantic moment kissing while cooking at  the Pedini Luxury kitchen. Prince Odi Okojie appeared as a guest by joining his wife, Mercy Johnson at Pedini cooking show. She wrote; “Something big is coming to you…..I cant wait…plus I had @princeodiokojie as a guest in my kitchen and it was so much fun…” Their marriage which has produced three children has been waxing stronger over the years. Source